# Funnel Config Schema

- Every funnel config must include: `id`, `slug`, `locale`, `accentColor`, `steps`.
- Each step must include: `id`, `title`, `path`, `componentOrder`, `content`.
- `componentOrder` values must match allowed component names from `src/funnels/types.ts`.
- Keep copy and section ordering in JSON, never hardcode marketing text inside route files.
- Step IDs must be unique within a funnel.
